<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>MMI recognizes and accepts college credit earned, with a grade of C or higher, through dual enrollment programs.  Students must request a transcript be sent from the college conferring the credit to the MMI Registrar's Office.  The transcript will be reviewed and appropriate credit assigned.  MMI will review also credit earned, with a grade of 3 or higher, through the Advanced Placement Program of the College Board (AP).  Students should request an official copy of their AP scores be sent to MMI's Registrar's Office.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.marionmilitary.edu/academics/academics-catalog.da" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

